Membership at Old Marsh Golf Club
Old Marsh members are part of a vision where golf and nature exist harmoniously.
Membership at Old Marsh is by invitation only and the number of equity memberships is strictly limited to less than 300. Both residents and nonresidents enjoy the exclusivity that ensures that Old Marsh will always provide its members with the traditional advantage of a private club in a friendly atmosphere, with people who are passionate about the finest traditions of the game.
Membership Information Request
Please complete the form below for more information. You will receive additional information about the club via email once the form is submitted.
